    BundleNode

    RootXMLNode<T>
    This interface defines all the protocol associated with a root node of an XML file.
    SubNode<T>
    This is the base interface for the JndiEnvRefNodes like ServiceReferenceNode so that the implementation can lie in their respective modules
    VersionUpgrade
    This interface defines the processing used to upgrade an older configuration file to the latest version.

    This interface defines the protocol associated with all the nodes.
